# Nezu Design System

Before changing UI, layout, motion, images, or copy structure, read `design-system/DESIGN.md`.

Use the existing visual language:
- Warm iMessage-native social helper.
- Brand blue for action, lemon yellow for emotional emphasis.
- Playfair Display for major headlines, Inter for UI/body text.
- Apple-like glass navigation, soft rounded cards, and slow floating doodles.
- Mobile-first spacing and responsive adjustments.

Prefer existing patterns in `components/ui/`, `components/sections/`, `lib/content.ts`, `public/images/`, and `public/scribbles/`.

If a change intentionally expands the visual system, update `design-system/DESIGN.md` in the same work.
